product_name: Vibram FiveFingers KMD Sport Shoes - Women's - 2013 Closeout
long_description: Made for running and fitness, the women's Vibram FiveFingers KMD Sport Shoes supply traction, support and a snug, personalized fit to accommodate your high-energy athleticism. Seamless 2mm polyurethane footbeds reduce friction underfoot. Heel and instep rip-and-stick closures help anchor the stretch nylon uppers to the contours of your feet for a seamless fit and completely natural feel. 4mm Vibram outsoles are made of nonmarking Vibram TC1 rubber and feature traction pods that follow the contours of your feet and toes for enhanced traction. Antimicrobial sockliners help deter odors. Vibram FiveFingers KMD Sport Shoes are machine washable in cold water; air dry only. Closeout.
